NYAA DL
Automatization of downloading anime episodes one by one from the site nyaa.si.

It's useful when you wanna watch anime that's still airing.

How to use
	- Install python3 and python3-pip
	- Make sure they're accessible as /usr/bin/python and /usr/bin/pip
	- Install qBittorrent
	- Launch it
	- Go to Tools > Preferences > Web UI
	- Check in "Web User Interface (Remote control)"
	- Change "IP address" to 127.0.0.1
	- Change "Port" to 1317
	- Check in "Bypass authentication for clients on localhost"
	- Click Apply
	- Run install.sh as root
	- Enjoy your anime!

